        "culturalTip": "'쭉'은 '계속', 'all the way'를 의미해요.",
        "explanationEn": "This is a basic directional guide used for giving directions.",
        "whenToUseEn": "\"When giving directions\"",
        "culturalTipEn": "The word '쭉' means 'continuously' or 'all the way.'"
